{"tid":1507020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB廣告有人搞 港鐵廣告無人搞？","createTime":"2019-08-26T03:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T04:21:31.000Z","uid":159596,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4c8239bc21555bc9b5f660e0ca1b5f622d1725e6","tid":1507020,"uid":159596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:57:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">絕對唔鼓勵做犯法嘢</span></span><br />\n但係貼下memo紙, poster響燈箱度<br />\n最多都係亂抛垃圾，違反港鐵附例<br />\n但係貼滿晒搞到遮住個燈箱<br />\n個廣告無晒效仲有冇必要投資落去呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更進一步嘅方法就靠大家諗啦<br />\n我就淨係識貼紙仔啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e9d3baff4b8f4b484f486ba8e53a01657e3f7f","tid":1507020,"uid":156791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:58:10.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"712e3b95ba37d0aa05caa4e2dc65c7a3772c2224","tid":1507020,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:58:21.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505474</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogleDrive: 91機場文宣資源 (手足有新貨話我知，會Upload上去)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=1038bc6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#推到有英文文宣#</span></strong></span><br />\n----------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>英文文宣建議：</strong></span><br />\n內容:<br />\n91 Hong Kong International Airport<br />\nSOS: Humanitarian Crisis Alert<br />\nGovernment has failed us. Police shot us.<br />\nIt&rsquo;s now or never, please stand with HK.<br />\nThanks in advance for your support and understanding.<br />\n<br />\n方向/ 建議：<br />\n-強調事態之緊急及嚴重<br />\n-形式係事先通知，而非道歉，機場示威是出師有名同埋其中既正當性<br />\n-例如可用&rdquo;SOS&rdquo;之字眼<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt9LBCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt9LBCx.jpg&h=73c530e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3kZESP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3kZESP.jpg&h=ba0a90fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wVcXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wVcXg.jpg&h=05fc61c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLLrqSL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLLrqSL.jpg&h=724c5863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfa2c0870255221f34c4cdba337390885a05c1bc","tid":1507020,"uid":159596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:58:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推到有人集思廣益"},{"pid":"3a9fae4289b2454120c4cb225003b3559eac4968","tid":1507020,"uid":159596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:59:12.000Z","msg":"推到有人集思廣益"},{"pid":"0771027b408f2639b273c582c6cb0a49f6749ca0","tid":1507020,"uid":159596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:59:25.000Z","msg":"推到有人集思廣益"},{"pid":"e2f4f1785a5290f4ee8013f4a75b4433a1624309","tid":1507020,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply